543
00:22:58,240 --> 00:23:00,180
[SPEAKER_00] Može biti da si nastradao,

544
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] da si žrtva i tako.

545
00:23:00,980 --> 00:23:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ustraješ ome, ja sam žrtva, ja sam žrtva, ja sam žrtva,

546
00:23:04,039 --> 00:23:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek svaki napadar, svaki agresor,

547
00:23:06,519 --> 00:23:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] počeo je s tim, ja sam žrtva.

548
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam pravo to.

549
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] Može se izaći s toga.

550
00:23:10,380 --> 00:23:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] Može se izaći sa opraštanjem,

551
00:23:12,579 --> 00:23:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] sa ulaženjem u to.

552
00:23:14,559 --> 00:23:17,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš biti žrtva ako nećeš.

553
00:23:17,180 --> 00:23:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ti vjeruješ njemu, vjeruješ da te on voli.

554
00:23:19,099 --> 00:23:20,339
[SPEAKER_00] I on ti kaže, ti si žrtva,

555
00:23:20,339 --> 00:23:21,240
[SPEAKER_00] jadan ti, jadan ti,

556
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:23,200
[SPEAKER_00] onda ga ti držiš pod mišku, ti džavol.

557
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] On ti govori, ti si žrtva, ti ga držiš

558
00:23:25,019 --> 00:23:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ne želiš ga pustiti.

559
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] Jer dok si žrtva, nisi odgovoran.

560
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš učuti je skopu odgovornosti,

561
00:23:31,279 --> 00:23:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] odluke za svoj, jer ja sam žrtva,

562
00:23:32,579 --> 00:23:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] ja tako, meni je teško.

563
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko puta džavol, tako ništa.

564
00:23:36,619 --> 00:23:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš jedan savjez s njime.

565
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam žrtva, ja sam žrtva.

566
00:23:39,619 --> 00:23:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] Strašno je to, ne.

567
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ili neko drugi, ne znam.

568
00:23:43,619 --> 00:23:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] Na razne načine,

569
00:23:45,319 --> 00:23:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] kako te drži pod mišku.

570
00:23:46,819 --> 00:23:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] Neki, ili ne želiš uprostiti,

571
00:23:49,140 --> 00:23:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] ili će ti uzeti neki novac,

572
00:23:51,160 --> 00:23:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] tri želi novac od tebe.

573
00:23:52,259 --> 00:23:53,259
[SPEAKER_00] O, ja ne smiješ to.

574
00:23:53,259 --> 00:23:55,319
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ima.

575
00:23:55,319 --> 00:23:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] Nađi ti, gdje je tvoj savez,

576
00:23:57,519 --> 00:23:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] tajni sa žalom,

577
00:23:59,019 --> 00:24:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] da ideš u crkvu, sve lijepo,

578
00:24:00,559 --> 00:24:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] svetas Boži, to je sveto,

579
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] to je sve lijepo,

580
00:24:02,619 --> 00:24:05,259
[SPEAKER_00] ali nećeš ti nas uništiti.

581
00:24:05,259 --> 00:24:07,759
[SPEAKER_00] Našu tajnu, ljubavnu vezu.

582
00:24:07,759 --> 00:24:09,279
[SPEAKER_00] Daje Bože, smiljuj na se

583
00:24:09,279 --> 00:24:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] da se uništi naša ljubavna veza

584
00:24:11,559 --> 00:24:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] sa onim što je tamo,

585
00:24:13,599 --> 00:24:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] što nas uništava,

586
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] što nas svara, što nas slaže.

587
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] Smiljuj na se, Kriste,

588
00:24:17,059 --> 00:24:18,700
[SPEAKER_00] izbavi nas iz kraljestva tame

589
00:24:18,700 --> 00:24:21,019
[SPEAKER_00] i prenesi u svoje divno kraljestvo svjetla.

590
00:24:21,019 --> 00:24:21,700
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

